# FERmentor frontend — environment variables
#
# Base URL of the FERmentor backend API (FastAPI).
# When this is UNSET (commented out / empty), the app serves data from the
# built-in mock layer (src/api/mock.ts) so the UI works without a backend.
#
# To point the frontend at the real backend, set this to the backend origin
# (no trailing slash). The client appends the "/api/..." paths itself.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
